<section data-label="20 Voorbeeld 04 · Mailbox doorzoeken">
  <div class="slide-frame split">

    <div style="flex: 1; padding: var(--pad-top) 80px var(--pad-bottom) var(--pad-x); display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 20px;">
        <span style="font-size: 88px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--accent); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.03em;">04</span>
        <span class="eyebrow">Voorbeeld</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bs-pills" style="margin-top: 22px;">
        <span class="bs-pill" style="--c: #06b6d4;">LLM</span>
        <span class="bs-pill" style="--c: #4f6cf7;">RAG</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="title" style="margin-top: 24px;">Je mailbox, plots doorzoekbaar<br/>in natuurlijke taal.</h2>
      <p class="body" style="margin-top: 32px;">
        Duizenden mails, verspreid over jaren. Vraag gewoon wat je zoekt en de AI geeft het antwoord met de juiste mail erbij.
      </p>

      <div style="margin-top: 56px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 32px;">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--ink-4);">Tot het antwoord</div>
          <div style="font-size: 64px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); margin-top: 8px; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; letter-spacing: -0.03em;">Seconden</div>
          <div class="small">in plaats van zelf zoeken</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--ink-4);">Elk antwoord</div>
          <div style="font-size: 64px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); margin-top: 8px; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; letter-spacing: -0.03em;">met bron</div>
          <div class="small">de juiste mail erbij, niets verzonnen</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div style="flex: 0 0 760px; background: var(--bg-alt); padding: 80px 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
      <!-- chat mockup — grounded in your mailbox -->
      <div style="width: 100%; max-width: 560px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-soft); border-radius: 24px; box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(15,23,42,0.10); overflow: hidden;">

        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; padding: 22px 26px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);">
          <div style="width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(8,145,178,0.12); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0891b2" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m2 7 10 6 10-6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.1;">AI-assistent</div>
            <div style="font-size: 20px; color: var(--ink-4);">met je mailbox</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 26px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;">
          <div style="align-self: flex-end; max-width: 84%; background: var(--accent); color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px 16px 4px 16px; padding: 16px 20px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.4;">
            Wat sprak ik met Verhulst af over de leverdatum?
          </div>

          <div style="align-self: flex-start; max-width: 92%; background: var(--bg-alt); color: var(--ink-2); border-radius: 16px 16px 16px 4px; padding: 18px 22px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.45;">
            Je bevestigde 14 maart als uiterste leverdatum, met 5 werkdagen marge.
            <div style="margin-top: 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;">
              <span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-soft); border-radius: 999px; padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 19px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; align-self: flex-start;">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m2 7 10 6 10-6"/></svg>
                Re: Levering Q1 · Verhulst NV · 8 feb
              </span>
              <span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-soft); border-radius: 999px; padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 19px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; align-self: flex-start;">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m2 7 10 6 10-6"/></svg>
                Bevestiging planning · 12 feb
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; padding: 18px 22px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft);">
          <div style="flex: 1; background: var(--bg-alt); border-radius: 999px; padding: 14px 22px; font-size: 21px; color: var(--ink-4);">Zoek in je mailbox…</div>
          <div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--accent); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="5"/><polyline points="5 12 12 5 19 12"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="chrome">
      <div class="sa-brand"><img src="assets/logo.svg" alt="">Smart<span class="accent">Agents</span></div>
      <div>20 / 32</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
